{"tid":752735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多倫多爆大型槍擊案　傳25下槍聲1死13傷","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T14:44:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6e61fbbebb2dcbd1133812b503e7ffb7a1726f","tid":752735,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/photo/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180723124238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180723124238&h=24630e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大多倫多希臘城（Greektown）於當地時間周日（22日）晚發生大型槍擊案，現場最少傳出25下槍聲，民眾慌忙走避，事件造成1名民眾死亡，13人中槍受傷送院，包括一名小童。有指槍手曾向警方開槍，然後自殺。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者表示晚上約10時，聽到當地一間知名餐廳外傳來多下槍聲，警方接報後趕到現場，封鎖附近街道，指示地鐵切勿在案發現場附近的地鐵站停站，同時呼籲民眾遠離事發區域。警方在現場成立指揮中心，派巴士接載目擊者到鄰近警局錄口供。<br />\n<br />\n事後有女目擊者在社交網Twitter表示，本來正享受一個美好的晚上，直至聽到連串槍聲，她慨嘆：「十分可怕，加拿大的槍械暴力真是瘋狂。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/photo/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_02b.jpg?20180723124238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20180723124238&h=9099f290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有持槍警員護送民眾離開。（美聯社圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/photo/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_03b.jpg?20180723124238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20180723124238&h=11bc97b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/photo/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_04b.jpg?20180723124238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20180723124238&h=20a4a0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180723%2Fbknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001.html&d=7PxwOGkTbeXZjwJBTQNWwbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=6be4252a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180723/bknint-20180723111155833-0723_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5a17abbe536fa52f00747dd02a61c48dba37b32c","tid":752735,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:27:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb139147192cdc39afe7daeb6b718242e1dc4887","tid":752735,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"死幾個人part and parcel - Sadiq Khan 倫敦南亞人市長"}]}